divs: Sighting Detailsjust a white ball no lights just going east a cross the sky no sound it was movning very fast.we see airplanes all the time .this was not a airplane mybe a big white balloon it went across the sky faster than a airplane. a group of us was setting in the back yard it was not dark out side i just looked up and seen it moving did not tell anyone that was setting there i said to my self that must be a ufo or satalite told my wife about it later. i looked up watch it for about 40 seconds going a cross sky untell it went out of sight on clouds in sky.the only reason im telling you about it mybe some one else saw it.that they were not the only one do not know what it was.
